## Completing Ideation

- Spec document is saved (in `<%= tickets_dir %>/docs/` or the ticket folder)
- Tickets are created in backlog
- Each ticket references the spec
- Ideas that didn't make the cut are documented as `bobby idea "..."` for future consideration
